required_fields.{first_name}: Text input field for child's first name
required_fields.{middle_name}: Text input field for child's middle name
required_fields.{last_name}: Text input field for child's last name
required_fields.{day}: Text input field for the day of the child's birth
required_fields.{month}: Text input field for the month of the child's birth
required_fields.{year}: Text input field for the year of the child's birth
required_fields.{bo}: Text input field for birth order (first, second, third, etc.)
required_fields.{fe}: Checkbox to mark with X if child is female
required_fields.{ma}: Checkbox to mark with X if child is male
required_fields.{tb1}: Related to 'Total number of children born alive' field
required_fields.{tb2}: Related to 'Total number of children born alive' field
required_fields.{tb3}: Related to 'Total number of children born alive' field
required_fields.{wab}: Text input field for child's weight at birth in grams
required_fields.{placebirth_host}: Text input field for the name of the hospital/clinic/institution/house number, street, barangay where the child was born
required_fields.{pb_city/mnplt}: Text input field for the city/municipality where the child was born
required_fields.{pb_prov}: Text input field for the province where the child was born
required_fields.{tncba }: Text input field for total number of children born alive to mother
required_fields.{ncslib}: Text input field for number of children still living including this birth to mother
required_fields.{ncbobnd}: Text input field for number of children born alive but now dead to mother
required_fields.{ftb}: Text input field for father’s age at the time of this birth (years)
required_fields.{mtb}: Text input field for mother’s age at the time of this birth (years)
required_fields.{province}: Text input field for the province of residence
required_fields.{city/mnplt}: Text input field for the city/municipality of residence
required_fields.{residence}: Text input field for parents' residence (House No., Street, Barangay)
required_fields.{m_prov}: Text input field for parents' province of residence
required_fields.{m_city/mnplt}: Text input field for parents' city/municipality of residence
required_fields.{m_first_name}: Text input field for mother's first name
required_fields.{m_middle_name}: Text input field for mother's middle name
required_fields.{m_last_name}: Text input field for mother's last name
required_fields.{m_citizenship}: Text input field for mother's citizenship
required_fields.{m_religion}: Text input field for mother's religion
required_fields.{m_occupation}: Text input field for mother's occupation
required_fields.{f_first_name}: Text input field for father's first name
required_fields.{f_middle_name}: Text input field for father's middle name
required_fields.{f_last_name}: Text input field for father's last name
required_fields.{f_citizenship}: Text input field for father's citizenship
required_fields.{f_religion}: Text input field for father's religion
required_fields.{f_occupation}: Text input field for father's occupation
required_fields.{imb1}: Checkbox to mark with X if multiple birth and child was first born
required_fields.{imb2}: Checkbox to mark with X if multiple birth and child was second born (twin)
required_fields.{imb3}: Checkbox to mark with X if multiple birth and child was triplet, etc.
required_fields.{imb_o}: Text input field to specify if multiple birth is 'Others'
required_fields.{at1}: Checkbox to mark with X if attendant was a Physician
required_fields.{at2}: Checkbox to mark with X if attendant was a Nurse
required_fields.{at3}: Checkbox to mark with X if attendant was a Midwife
required_fields.{at4}: Checkbox to mark with X if attendant was 'Others'
required_fields.{at5}: Text input field to specify if attendant was 'Others'
required_fields.{cob_t}: This template is not used in the context for OCR extraction or to fill.
required_fields.{cob_print}: Text input field for printed name in the certification of birth section
required_fields.{cob_title}: Text input field for title/position in the certification of birth section
required_fields.{cob_address}: Text input field for address in the certification of birth section
required_fields.{cob_date}: Text input field for date in the certification of birth section
required_fields.{informant_name}: Text input field for name of informant
required_fields.{informant_relation}: Text input field for informant's relationship to the child
required_fields.{informant_address}: Text input field for informant's address
required_fields.{informant_date}: Text input field for the date the informant signed the form
required_fields.{prepared_by_name}: Text input field for the name of the person who prepared the birth certificate
required_fields.{prepared_by_position}: Text input field for the position/title of the person who prepared the birth certificate
required_fields.{prepared_by_date}: Text input field for the date the birth certificate was prepared
required_fields.{receive_by_name}: Text input field for the name of the person who received the birth certificate at the Civil Registrar's office
required_fields.{receive_by_title}: Text input field for the title/position of the person who received the birth certificate at the Civil Registrar's office
required_fields.{receive_by_date}: Text input field for the date the birth certificate was received at the Civil Registrar's office
required_fields.{registration_n}: Text input field for registry number
required_fields.{date_place_marriage_parents}: Text input field for date and place of marriage of parents
